quran[6{c,v,t}:
2,164,be shak asmano aur zameen ke peda karne mein aur raat aur din ke aik dosray ke peechay anay jaane mein aur kashtiyon aur jahazoo mein jo darya mein logon ke faiday ki cheeze le kar rawan hain aur meen mein jis ko khuda aasman se brsata aur is se zameen ko marnay ke baad zindah ( yani khushk hue peechay sirsabz ) kardaita hai aur zameen par har qisam ke janwar phelanay mein aur hawaon ke chalanay mein aur baadalon mein jo aasman aur zameen ke darmain ghiry rehtay hain. aqalmandon ke liye ( khuda ki qudrat ki ) nishanain hain
2,165,aur baaz log aisay hain jo ghair khuda ko shareek ( khuda ) banatay aur un se khuda ki si mohabbat karte hain. lekin jo imaan walay hain woh to khuda hi ke sab se ziyada Dostdar hain. aur ae kash zalim log jo baat azaab ke waqt dekhen ge ab dekh letay ke sab terhan ki taaqat khuda hi ko hai. aur yeh ke khuda sakht azaab karne wala hai
2,166,is din ( kufar ke ) peshwa apne pairon se bezari zahir karen ge aur ( dono ) azaab ( Ellahi ) dekh len ge aur un ke aapas ke taluqaat munhqita ho jaien ge
2,167,( yeh haal dekh kar ) pairwi karne walay ( hasrat se ) kahin ge ke ae kash hamein phir duniya mein jana naseeb ho taakay jis terhan yeh hum se bezaar ho rahay hain isi terhan hum bhi un se bezaar hon. isi terhan khuda un ke aamaal inhen hasrat bana kar dukhaay gaavr woh dozakh se nikal nahi saken ge
2,168,logo jo cheeze zameen mein halal Tayyab hain woh khao. aur shetan ke qadmon par nah chalo. woh tumhara khula dushman hai
2,169,woh to tum ko buraiee aur be hiyai hi ke kaam karne ko kehta hai aur yeh bhi ke khuda ki nisbat aisi baatein kaho jin ka tumhe ( kuch bhi ) ilm nahi
